    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📥 Receive & Acknowledge Click\nReceives the POST from Slack when a recruiter clicks a button on the action card. **Acknowledge Slack** fires in parallel (not after) – Slack needs a 200 response within **3 seconds** or it shows a red error to the user, even if the rest succeeds.",
