    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔍 Parse Slack Action Payload\nSlack sends the click as `application/x-www-form-urlencoded` with a single `payload` field containing JSON. This node unpacks it, extracts the action ID, user info, and the candidate JSON we stuffed into the Save button's `value` field back in Workflow A.",
        "height": 416,
