      "name": "Sticky Note2"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 💾 Save to Sheet\nFlattens the nested candidate JSON into 30 discrete columns (`role1_title`, `role1_company`, etc.) so the Sheet stays sortable and filterable. Appends a new row, then edits the Slack card via `response_url` to confirm \"✅ Saved by @user\" – no extra Slack OAuth scopes needed.",
